Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底是买了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自从新国王即位以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}衣料服饰也逐渐充足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要挑选都费了我好大功夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 是么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要穿衣服啰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女孩子可不能让身体着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“好”只要说一次就行啰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉衣褶好多 好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HCE7CB3&,&HE9D3ED&,&HFAD0D4&,&HF9D4CF&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(184,348)}艾尔奇亚国民淑女推荐服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蕾丝就是为了女孩子而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样子能做好女仆的工作么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要穿成这样待在身边 大家就会幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HC5BFDD&,&HE9D3ED&,&HB5A7CB&,&HF9D4CF&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(152,342)}艾尔奇亚国内家政妇推荐服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这衣服貌似胸部越小的人越适合穿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.75,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HEDD67F&,&HEDDCA4&,&HA05D4C&,&HDFC7DF&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(114,324)}艾尔奇亚国民少女游泳推荐服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要脱 我现在就要脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兔子的兽人种？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}克拉米一穿上 野兽便超越了神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:03.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&H8765B5&,&H8A5B92&,&H9EBE87&,&HA1DF85&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(114,324)}艾尔奇亚国民女员工推荐服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}容易活动 这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对冒失的克拉米来说 或许正适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:10.31,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HF7D4AE&,&HFAE0EB&,&HDAACAF&,&HA1DF85&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(114,324)}艾尔奇亚国民女童体育推荐服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 这件真合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 那是小孩子的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:17.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HC36089&,&HC2B0CA&,&H9384AF&,&HD8C9E7&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(138,344)}艾尔奇亚国学校女童学生服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你故意的吧 绝对是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 下面呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会走光的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但就是这点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:25.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs80\1vc(&HEEC0D5&,&HC3D7E4&,&HEBCDE4&,&HA297D9&)\3c&H841E4A&\pos(26,298)}艾尔奇亚国王即位\N\N纪念商品销售第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是国王的品牌店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无论哪件都Good Job啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 菲你只是拿我当玩具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}克拉米从小就只能穿破旧粗糙的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直都想让克拉米穿上各式各样的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这只是我单方面的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过这个先不说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在感冒以前 要先把衣服弄干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一开始就用魔法弄干不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 你果然是在玩我…
